About Us

J-Famade Agrofarm is one of the largest central regional wholesalers of nutraceuticals, green food supplements, agricultural fertilizer, and animal healthcare formulations. Our organic, eco-friendly, and ayurvedically proven products deliver safe nourishment for the community, crop, and chicken.

With market-ready products and personalized packaging solutions, we help customers build a brand faster, better, and more successful than others.

MISSION

Work closely with clients to provide the best farm products, services, and solutions to farmers.

VISION

Become a national recognizable and reliable brand for animal and plant nutrition.
